Bongani Mahlangu, provincial traffic officer Piet Mthsweni’s brother, reported him missing after last seeing him waiting for an unknown man near a Siyathuthuka tavern. Mr Mthsweni was wearing a black ANC branded jacket before his disappearance. According to the SAPS, Mr Mthsweni never divulged the identity of the person he was waiting to meet. Since his disappearance, Mr Mthsweni’s cell phone cannot be reached.
He has also not made any attempt to contact family or friends. People with information about his whereabouts can call 013 253 1687 or Detective Constable Mike Mnisi directly on 067 309 4507.